
<h1>Your Search Results For:</h1>

<% if @new_search %>
  <h1>You need to fill in each search box. Try again? </h1>
<% else %>
  <%= @vehicle.year %> <%= @vehicle.brand.name %> <%= @vehicle.model %> <i><%= @part %></i> View <%= link_to "vehicle", @vehicle %><br>

<div class="col-md-12">
  <div class="tabs-container">
      <ul class="nav nav-tabs">
          <li class="active"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-1"> Compatible Parts <span class="badge"> <%= @compatible_search_results.count %></span></a></li>
          <li class=""><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-2">Potential Parts <span class="badge">2</span></a></li>
          <li class=""><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-3">OEM Parts <span class="badge"> <%= @oem_search_results.count %></span></a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="tab-content">
          <div id="tab-1" class="tab-pane active">
              <div class="panel-body">
                  <strong>These are compatiple parts to your search.</strong>
                  <% if @compatible_search_results || @backwards_compatible_search_results %>
                    <%= render partial: 'compatibles/compatible', collection: @compatible_search_results %>
                    <%= render partial: 'compatibles/backwards_compatible', collection: @backwards_compatible_search_results %>
                    <% end %>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div id="tab-2" class="tab-pane">
              <div class="panel-body">
                  <strong>Thesea are Potential Parts - This is calculated with some nifty algorithm magic.</strong>

                  <p>Thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects
                      and flies, then I feel the presence of the Almighty, who formed us in his own image, and the breath </p>

                  <p>I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite
                      sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment; and yet.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div id="tab-3" class="tab-pane">
              <div class="panel-body">
                  <strong>These are OEM parts - just for your information.</strong>
                  <% if @oem_search_results %>
                    <%= render partial: 'parts/oem_part', collection: @oem_search_results %>
                  <% end %>
              </div>
          </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>
